        "TileImage": "$($repository 7762eb11-138c-4d5b-bf3c-f28921cfa0e0).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening agent whatever.\r\rIntel tells that Alma Reynard is having her joyful night. However, Our client does not like it. Client claims that Alma Reynard is his only partner, originally. And points that Alma Reynard is cheating on the client. So the client wants us to eliminate Alma Reynard except the man.\r\rAnother intel, agent. Alma Reynard also had several &quot;pleasurable&quot; night with her bodyguards. And the client wants us to eliminate them too.\r\rI hope you are loyal to your partner, agent.",
